    "MindfulPacer can remind you to reflect on your activities, energy management, moods and symptoms, for example at specific times or when a biometric value (such as your heart rate or steps) reaches a certain threshold.\n\nPlease allow MindfulPacer to send notifications to receive the reflection reminders." : {

    },
    "MindfulPacer can visualize your biometric data (as measured by your Apple Watch) and visualize it together with your diary entries in the Analysis page.\n\nPlease allow MindfulPacer to access your Apple Health data. Select the biometric data that you want to share (e.g. heart rate and/or steps)." : {

    },
